.row
  .col-sm-6.max-height
    h3.title Project manager
    .editor-1.content
      p
        strong Job Description
      p The Project Manager is responsible for planning, executing and evaluating projects according to timelines and budgets.  The PM is the bridge between the client and the development team, ensuring the client expectations are well implemented within budget.
      p
        strong Work Requirement
      p Assist in the definition of project scope and requirements, involving all relevant stakeholders and ensuring technical feasibility
      p Develop a detailed project plan to monitor and track progress
      p Track project progress ensuring highest quality of work
      p Successfully manage the relationship with the client and all stakeholders by excellent communication
      p Manage changes to the project scope, project schedule, and project costs
      p Create and maintain comprehensive project documentation
      p Perform risk management to minimize project risks
      p
        strong Required Skills
      p Background and understanding of software development
      p Knowledge of prevailing web and mobile technology
      p Excellent communication skill and client handling skills
      p Solid organizational skills including attention to detail and multi-tasking skills
      p Good English communication skills is a plus
      p
        strong Benefits
      p Great chance to develop your skills and competences, with in-house skill and English training
      p Successful candidates will be offered a friendly, dynmic working environment in Sutrix Media
      p Opportunities for promotions and career development in a fast growing company
